20
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:28,440
Yi Xinran.

21
00:01:33,039 --> 00:01:34,120
Yi Xinran.

22
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,280
Get down.

23
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:40,520
Move aside.

24
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,720
My position.

25
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,759
Are you crazy, Guan Ling?

26
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:54,800
