39
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:48,960
Qingkong

40
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:51,320
Why did you look for me?

41
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:53,720
Yi Xinran said she doesn't like me anymore.

42
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:54,960
I want you to help me.

43
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,220
Make her like me again.

44
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,240
