45
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:00,940
Bring some snacks.

46
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:01,940
Mm-hmm.

47
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,360
First,

48
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:09,880
find important places

49
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:11,280
