56
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,440
It's really hot today.

57
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:59,480
If only there was a little breeze right now.

58
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:03,920
Finally,

59
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,520
create a surprise.

60
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:07,370
Just like in Korean dramas.

61
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,400
Korean dramas?

62
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,480
Blow that way, blow that way.

63
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,400
Harder.

64
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,240
